  "detailed_description": "You drive a car when a UFO crosses the road. You get abducted, but what comes next is not what you expect.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2719950/extras/791b53460cadb550860a0c205dfed14f.poster.avif?t=1733217049\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2719950/extras/791b53460cadb550860a0c205dfed14f.webm?t=1733217049\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2719950/extras/791b53460cadb550860a0c205dfed14f.mp4?t=1733217049\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>It's an enigmatic trip of your mind towards the mind of the Other. It has something to say to you. Will you listen? Will you understand?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2719950/extras/47a908f6842e6a3cb72d6fa51615175a.poster.avif?t=1733217049\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2719950/extras/47a908f6842e6a3cb72d6fa51615175a.webm?t=1733217049\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2719950/extras/47a908f6842e6a3cb72d6fa51615175a.mp4?t=1733217049\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The gameplay of \"Unveiling\" is simple and the puzzles are unobtrusive. You move through mind-bending environments, wrapped in striking visuals, and interact with pieces of the story.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2719950/extras/6aaf30513d572cb3059eea1b4db1947f.poster.avif?t=1733217049\" width=576 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2719950/extras/6aaf30513d572cb3059eea1b4db1947f.webm?t=1733217049\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2719950/extras/6aaf30513d572cb3059eea1b4db1947f.mp4?t=1733217049\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>This 30-minute experience is inspired by the love of sci-fi and the resurgence of UFO/UAP in the modern psyche. It explores a moment of contact and the possible motives of Non-Human Intelligence.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2719950/extras/f22f2037183b1da27b354859f26f20cf.poster.avif?t=1733217049\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2719950/extras/f22f2037183b1da27b354859f26f20cf.webm?t=1733217049\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2719950/extras/f22f2037183b1da27b354859f26f20cf.mp4?t=1733217049\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "You drive a car when a UFO crosses the road. You get abducted, but what comes next is not what you expect.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2719950/extras/791b53460cadb550860a0c205dfed14f.poster.avif?t=1733217049\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2719950/extras/791b53460cadb550860a0c205dfed14f.webm?t=1733217049\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2719950/extras/791b53460cadb550860a0c205dfed14f.mp4?t=1733217049\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>It's an enigmatic trip of your mind towards the mind of the Other. It has something to say to you. Will you listen? Will you understand?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2719950/extras/47a908f6842e6a3cb72d6fa51615175a.poster.avif?t=1733217049\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2719950/extras/47a908f6842e6a3cb72d6fa51615175a.webm?t=1733217049\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2719950/extras/47a908f6842e6a3cb72d6fa51615175a.mp4?t=1733217049\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The gameplay of \"Unveiling\" is simple and the puzzles are unobtrusive. You move through mind-bending environments, wrapped in striking visuals, and interact with pieces of the story.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2719950/extras/6aaf30513d572cb3059eea1b4db1947f.poster.avif?t=1733217049\" width=576 height=242 ><source src=\"https